00:44:14,100 --> 00:44:16,180
long weekends

935
00:44:16,180 --> 00:44:18,340
good vacations

936
00:44:18,340 --> 00:44:21,020
grow old healthy

937
00:44:21,020 --> 00:44:22,660
have a fun retirement

938
00:44:22,660 --> 00:44:25,220
die easy, no hell

939
00:44:25,220 --> 00:44:29,460
and that's all you want

940
00:44:29,460 --> 00:44:32,060
You don't give a rip

941
00:44:32,060 --> 00:44:37,780
whether your life counts on this earth for eternity

942
00:44:37,780 --> 00:44:41,420
That's a tragedy in the making

943
00:44:41,420 --> 00:44:43,740
That is a tragedy in the making

944
