About three weeks ago

945
00:44:45,500 --> 00:44:47,820
we got news at our church

946
00:44:47,820 --> 00:44:55,820
that Ruby Eliason and Laura Edwards

947
00:44:55,820 --> 00:45:02,300
were killed in Cameroon

948
00:45:02,300 --> 00:45:05,180
Ruby Eliason

949
00:45:05,180 --> 00:45:12,140
her 80, single all her life

950
00:45:12,140 --> 00:45:14,860
a nurse

951
00:45:14,860 --> 00:45:18,620
poured her life out for one thing

952
00:45:18,620 --> 00:45:21,740
to make Jesus Christ known

953
00:45:21,740 --> 00:45:24,540
among the sick and the poor

954
00:45:24,540 --> 00:45:28,860
in the hardest and most unreached place

955
00:45:28,860 --> 00:45:31,300
Laura Edwards

956
00:45:31,300 --> 00:45:34,300
medical doctor in the Twin Cities

957
00:45:34,300 --> 00:45:37,100
and then in retirement

958
00:45:37,100 --> 00:45:39,260
partnering up with Ruby

959
00:45:39,260 --> 00:45:42,460
also pushing 80

960
00:45:42,460 --> 00:45:46,500
and going village to village in Cameroon

961
00:45:46,500 --> 00:45:49,940
and the brakes give way

962
00:45:49,940 --> 00:45:52,420
over a cliff they go

963
00:45:52,420 --> 00:45:54,860
and they're dead instantly

964
00:45:54,860 --> 00:45:57,660
and I ask my people

965
00:45:57,660 --> 00:46:04,740
is this a tragedy

966
00:46:04,740 --> 00:46:08,340
two women

967
00:46:08,340 --> 00:46:12,820
in their 80s almost

968
00:46:12,820 --> 00:46:16,940
a whole life devoted to one idea

969
00:46:16,940 --> 00:46:20,060
Jesus Christ magnified

970
00:46:20,060 --> 00:46:23,220
among the poor and the sick

971
00:46:23,220 --> 00:46:27,820
in the hardest places

972
00:46:27,820 --> 00:46:29,660
at 20 years

973
00:46:29,660 --> 00:46:33,060
after most of their American counterparts

974
00:46:33,060 --> 00:46:35,540
