980
00:46:50,100 --> 00:46:53,180
I'll read you what a tragedy is

981
00:46:53,180 --> 00:46:55,740
We've got a little article here from

982
00:46:55,740 --> 00:46:57,740
Reader's Digest

983
00:46:57,740 --> 00:46:59,220
You don't read Reader's Digest

984
00:46:59,220 --> 00:47:01,940
I know that

985
00:47:01,940 --> 00:47:08,100
But there is a generation who does

986
00:47:08,100 --> 00:47:10,940
This is a tragedy

987
00:47:10,940 --> 00:47:13,660
