988
00:47:13,660 --> 00:47:17,260
Start Now, Retire Early

989
00:47:17,260 --> 00:47:19,980
February 1998

990
00:47:19,980 --> 00:47:24,460
Bob and Penny took early retirement

991
00:47:24,460 --> 00:47:26,420
