995
00:47:36,740 --> 00:47:41,220
where they cruise on their 30-foot trawler

996
00:47:41,220 --> 00:47:43,380
play softball

997
00:47:43,380 --> 00:47:46,820
and collect shells

998
00:47:50,020 --> 00:47:55,620
That's a tragedy

999
00:47:55,620 --> 00:47:57,740
And there are people in this country

1000
00:47:57,740 --> 00:48:00,580
that are spending billions of dollars

1001
00:48:00,580 --> 00:48:04,980
