1004
00:48:09,180 --> 00:48:11,540
Don't buy it

1005
00:48:11,540 --> 00:48:13,180
With all my heart

1006
00:48:13,180 --> 00:48:14,780
I plead with you

1007
00:48:14,780 --> 00:48:19,940
Don't buy that dream

1008
00:48:19,940 --> 00:48:23,100
The American dream

1009
00:48:23,100 --> 00:48:26,540
A nice house, a nice car

1010
00:48:26,540 --> 00:48:29,380
A nice job, a nice family

1011
00:48:29,380 --> 00:48:31,540
A nice retirement

1012
00:48:31,540 --> 00:48:35,820
Collecting shells

1013
00:48:35,820 --> 00:48:37,940
At the last chapter

1014
00:48:37,940 --> 00:48:39,700
Before you stand

1015
00:48:39,700 --> 00:48:42,300
Before the creator of the universe

1016
00:48:42,300 --> 00:48:46,060
To give an account with what you did

1017
00:48:46,060 --> 00:48:47,420
Here it is, Lord

1018
00:48:47,420 --> 00:48:51,900
My shell collection

1019
00:48:51,900 --> 00:48:53,300
Look, Lord

1020
00:48:53,300 --> 00:48:56,060
My shell collection

1021
00:48:56,060 --> 00:48:59,260
And I've got a good swing

1022
00:48:59,260 --> 00:49:03,460
And look at my boat

1023
00:49:03,460 --> 00:49:06,020
God

1024
00:49:06,020 --> 00:49:11,540
Look at my boat, God

1025
00:49:11,540 --> 00:49:13,260
Well, not for Ruby

1026
00:49:13,260 --> 00:49:17,860
And not for Laura

1027
00:49:17,860 --> 00:49:19,620
Don't waste your life

1028
00:49:19,620 --> 00:49:22,900
Don't waste it

1029
00:49:22,900 --> 00:49:26,220
不要浪費你的生命

1030
00:49:26,220 --> 00:49:30,660
唯有為基督而活而死的生命

1031
00:49:30,660 --> 00:49:32,580
纔是沒有浪費的

1032
